    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <i>Mr Trials</i>, a single-player, physics-based platformer with charming blocky graphics that bring a playful, retro feel to every level. Navigate intricate obstacles and perform thrilling stunts in vibrant, pixel-inspired environments. Perfect for players who love the challenge of mastering unique mechanics in a visually fun and stylized world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50 Challenging Levels:</strong> Each level is designed to test your abilities with increasing difficulty. Unlock new stages and explore diverse environments that bring fresh twists to every challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 Themed Worlds:</strong> Progress through themed worlds, each introducing new terrains, and environmental hazards. From desert dunes to icy peaks, each world demands a different strategy!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Golden Helmets:</strong> Outperform the regular score by hitting the highest stunt combos to earn the prestigious Golden Helmet on each level. Collect them all to show off your mastery!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to Learn, Hard to Master:</strong> With intuitive controls, you'll jump, flip, and balance with ease—but true mastery requires skill and precision. Only the best can complete every level with a perfect score!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to prove you’ve got what it takes to conquer every level, earn all the Golden Helmets, and become the ultimate stunt master in <i>Mr Trials</i>?</p>",
